          name: resourceGroupName
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method

            type: string

            maxLength: 90
            pattern: ^[-\w\._]+$
          examples:

          examples:

            type: string
          examples:

        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:

              examples:
